{"tid":2433261,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港人出左呢啲人真係羞愧","createTime":"2021-03-04T23:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T06:09:10.000Z","uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"daecd3ef140fcde17e2977aaf89238d6e829fd52","tid":2433261,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:40:06.000Z","msg":"有件事我發現左一段時間，就係而家自稱黃色嘅apps無論什麼<br />\n用什麼山又好真香港人又好時代什麼光榮什麼<br />\n啲人都係藍毛黑嚟<br />\n十次有十次都遇到<br />\n明顯又遇到<br />\n好常約你出去見面之後件事就不了了之一係就除咗用爛呢招<br />\n同用原始思想或弱智人士嘅方式對人<br />\n永遠唔見佢地啲人做到啲咩事。<br />\n一係就故意呃你出去搵機會做啲低能事<br />\n最常就加料<br />\n永遠做呢啲事扮到自己班人好高能好堅<br />\n其實同呢啲人講同一語言都覺得羞恥"},{"pid":"e4fbe4b7cdd8eeb6688f1e1f829155c5873dee51","tid":2433261,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:45:18.000Z","msg":"除咗五毛，香港藍屍佔咗4成，唔係絕對少數<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/76688985_961922030843084_5258187310687584256_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=3&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=AxO7edWzlDYAX-9oK7h&amp;_nc_oc=AQkVJDpElkH6UfyPAYTXEOtxsyAidPWvOqN2nhtwO3GfmhRmycIshytAGmpMtaBFUW8&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=198b305530787ad9dac35a240ddca6d5&amp;oe=60686875\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F76688985_961922030843084_5258187310687584256_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D3%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DAxO7edWzlDYAX-9oK7h%26_nc_oc%3DAQkVJDpElkH6UfyPAYTXEOtxsyAidPWvOqN2nhtwO3GfmhRmycIshytAGmpMtaBFUW8%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D198b305530787ad9dac35a240ddca6d5%26oe%3D60686875&h=59632b79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8d75bebb1f7d7b5585c03711e30cc8e8716d82f0","tid":2433261,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e4fbe4b7cdd8eeb6688f1e1f829155c5873dee51","tid":2433261,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T23:45:18.000Z","msg":"除咗五毛，香港藍屍佔咗4成，唔係絕對少數<br />\n<br />